response: Alright. Here's wild tic tac toe.Welcome to Wild Tic-tac-toe. In this game, players can choose to place either X or O on each move, anytime. You are trying to get three in a row first. To make a move respond with a symbol name and a place on the board. For example, say "move cross to the upper right corner". To start a new game at any time, say: who the first and start game. For example, say "You start first"
